{"tid":1792362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請一個落選區議員， 就拎 $100美金，支爆為止！！","createTime":"2019-12-21T14:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:47:36.000Z","uid":331459,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca437cbe10aa86642e4a24d57fcb8775d6a660","tid":1792362,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbGSs2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbGSs2b.png&h=d527fbc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">假設</span><br />\n政府請一個落選區議員, 我地就係銀行抽HKD$1,000出黎 (最好換埋美金! 放係屋企，唔用)<br />\n200萬手足入面, 只要10萬人幫手就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n100,000人 X $1,000=$100,000,000=$1億<br />\n每請一個=抽$1億=25000分一的M1<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十個就係2500分一的M1 (以十月數據, 而家應該唔只)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n一百個就GG，我都冇咁多$<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: gold;\">量力而為</span><br />\n<br />\n但見到佢地hea住袋我地啲錢就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">利申:</span>冇修ECON, 唔該經濟手足幫手check 數<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6gdXvA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6gdXvA.jpg&h=77944981&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0000d0256a0f7ac82abea50d25b5870b2e5d66af","tid":1792362,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"葉問生canncer，去美國幫仔搵學校，打贏晒班歧視支那人嘅鬼佬，同時李小龍既徒弟係美國得罪軍官，但軍官挑葉問機但打輸左，最後葉問返香港教仔詠春然後死咗。"},{"pid":"1c96bfe60275eeaffac5c980f3861b87c37378b2","tid":1792362,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"大家星期六有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<b